{{Top|leg}}
A '''barve''' was a small, six-legged animal raised for its meat. Their unclean reputation led to the word ''barve'', or adjective ''barvy'', being used across the galaxy as an [[List of phrases and slang/Legends|insult]]. The insult was especially prevalent among [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunters]]. The insult was also used to label [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] affected by [[force psychosis]], with people calling them "barvy Jedi".

